-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e72ec8-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Give an example use-case for middleware in Express.','[\"Examples include logging, authentication checks, parsing request bodies, input validation, and error handling middleware.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e8033c-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','What is the signature of an Express error-handling middleware?','[\"(err, req, res, next)\", \"(req, res, next, err)\", \"(req, res)\", \"(err, next)\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e84f61-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','An error-handling middleware must be added after other middleware and routes to catch their errors.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73e96d53-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which middleware parses incoming JSON payloads?','[\"express.json()\", \"express.body()\", \"bodyParser.text()\", \"express.urlencoded()\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ea56cf-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','You should enable body parsing middleware before defining routes that need access to req.body.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73eb005a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which Mongoose method saves a document instance to the database?','[\"doc.save()\", \"Model.insert()\", \"Model.createInstance()\", \"db.put()\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73eb57fb-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name a reason to use Mongoose schemas rather than raw MongoDB driver.','[\"Schemas provide structure, validation, middleware (hooks), and convenient model APIs which simplify development and reduce runtime errors.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ec04c7-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which HTTP method is typically used to update an existing resource partially?','[\"PATCH\", \"GET\", \"POST\", \"DELETE\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ec4e1a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','List the typical endpoints for a resource \'users\' in a CRUD API.','[\"GET /users, GET /users/:id, POST /users, PUT or PATCH /users/:id, DELETE /users/:id\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ece816-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which library is commonly used with Express for validation middleware?','[\"express-validator\", \"react-validate\", \"lodash.validate\", \"body-guard\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ed3292-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','Validation should always happen before writing to the database.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ede01a-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which pagination method is more performant for large datasets?','[\"cursor-based pagination\", \"offset-based pagination\", \"full-scan pagination\", \"page-number only pagination\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ee3627-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name one drawback of offset-based pagination.','[\"Offset pagination can be slow for large offsets and may return inconsistent results if the underlying dataset changes between requests.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73ef5d76-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which token type is commonly stored in localStorage for SPA auth (though with security caveats)?','[\"JWT\", \"Session ID cookie\", \"Opaque database key\", \"CSRF token\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73efb3d2-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Give one security risk of storing JWT in localStorage.','[\"LocalStorage is vulnerable to XSS; malicious scripts can read tokens and exfiltrate them.\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f06ca1-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which library is commonly used in Node to sign and verify JWTs?','[\"jsonwebtoken\", \"jwt-node\", \"express-jwt\", \"body-jwt\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f0b460-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','true_false','A JWT must be encrypted to be secure.','[\"True\", \"False\"]',1,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-14 23:42:41'),('73f14d7f-4fd5-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which package helps set secure HTTP headers in Express?','[\"helmet\", \"cors\", \"morgan\", \"express-rate-limit\"]',0,'2026-05-14 23:42:41','2026-05-1