monly used for API schemas that power Swagger UI?','[\"XML\", \"OpenAPI (JSON/YAML)\", \"CSV\", \"Markdown\"]',1,'2026-05-14 22:56:12','2026-05-14 22:56:12'),('f535792b-4fce-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','supertest is primarily used for:','[\"unit testing functions\", \"running e2e browser tests\", \"making HTTP assertions against an Express app\", \"linting code\"]',2,'2026-05-14 22:56:12','2026-05-14 22:56:12'),('f535fa58-4fce-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which tool is commonly used to collect metrics exposed by an app for scraping?','[\"Grafana\", \"Prometheus\", \"New Relic\", \"Kibana\"]',1,'2026-05-14 22:56:12','2026-05-14 22:56:12'),('f53674ab-4fce-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','written','Name one benefit of running your Express app inside a Docker container.','[\"consistent environment across development and production, easier deployment and isolation\"]',0,'2026-05-14 22:56:12','2026-05-14 22:56:12'),('f536fc70-4fce-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821','dde5cde4-4fcc-11f1-9abe-6c02e0d26821',NULL,'454cde6d-4f80-11f1-ba5b-00090ffe0001','multiple_choice','Which of these is a recommended step before deploying your API?','[\"Remove all logging\", \"Commit secrets to repo\", \"Run automated tests\", \"Disable authentication\"]',2,'2026-05-14 22:56:12','2026-05-14 22:56:12');
